# H4xxed Up For Barbecue

An entry into the Novermber/December [Bytebeat](http://canonical.org/%7Ekragen/bytebeat/) contest that won 2nd place at Master Level. Intended bitrate is 48khz and output range is Floatbeat (outputs between -1...1)

[Listen with the Dollchan Bytebeat player](https://dollchan.net/bytebeat/#)

Features a feedback-heavy stereo multitap detune delay, inspired partly by [Feeshbread's Dead Data reverb](https://www.reddit.com/r/bytebeat/comments/1fzb7eh/dead_data_my_entry_for_byte_battle_season_1/).
